tuxtools :

tuxtools is a collection of bash scripts and programs that make life easier when convertion tuxracer tracks to extreme tux racer tracks.
All code in this collections is licensed under the GPL version 3

in the folder "tcltotux" you can find a simple tool to convert tuxracer course files to extreme tux racer course files.

in the folder "bash" you can find some bash scripts that I use to automate conversion and adding entries
